Everteen has changed lives of hundred of Covid-19 pandemic affected women through its exciting initiative #PadHerLIfe 
Under this initiative, everteen is providing financial support upto Rs.50,000/- through its Neem & Safflower Sanitary Pads.
I feel extremely happy, that I participated in this initiative and contributed to provide our Indian household women a chance to restart their business and career.

You can register yourself for this initiative by visiting www.sheneedspad.com and by filling in the relevant details required.

Please share this message, video and help spread the word about this life-changing initiative as much as possible.
